knife was middle of it) a shot cut started. Vamprah
pressed her eyes, but she didn't more over move her
hear to other side and gave a little moan.

Necklance lights started bliked and, soon the shot cut
ended and the necklance opened.

Just cut untilthe middle was enoguh to messed the
necklance up, and in one of the opened sides fell a
small chip that have Predacon's symbol.
